---
title: "performUpkeep (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_paused: performUpkeep(performData) called
    q_check_paused --> q_check_role: contract not paused
    q_check_paused --> q_revert_paused: contract paused
    q_revert_paused --> [*]: revert Paused
    q_check_role --> q_check_asset_out: caller has AUCTION_WORKER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_revert_role: unauthorized
    q_revert_role --> [*]: revert Unauthorized
    q_check_asset_out --> q_decode: assetOut is configured
    q_check_asset_out --> q_revert_config: assetOut not configured
    q_revert_config --> [*]: revert AssetOutNotConfigured
    q_decode --> q_process_starts: decode performData into startList and endList
    q_process_starts --> q_validate_start: for asset in startList
    q_validate_start --> q_check_configured: validate asset
    q_check_configured --> q_check_no_live: asset is configured
    q_check_configured --> q_revert_asset: asset not configured
    q_revert_asset --> [*]: revert AssetNotConfigured
    q_check_no_live --> q_check_price_valid: no live auction for asset
    q_check_no_live --> q_revert_live: live auction exists
    q_revert_live --> [*]: revert AuctionAlreadyActive
    q_check_price_valid --> q_check_min_size: assetPrice and assetOutPrice valid
    q_check_price_valid --> q_revert_price: price invalid or stale
    q_revert_price --> [*]: revert InvalidPrice
    q_check_min_size --> q_start_auction: totalUsdValue >= minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_check_min_size --> q_revert_size: below minimum
    q_revert_size --> [*]: revert BelowMinAuctionSize
    q_start_auction --> q_transfer: set s_auctionStarts[asset] = block.timestamp
    q_transfer --> q_approve: transferForSwap from FeeAggregator
    q_approve --> q_next_start: approve CowSwap VaultRelayer for asset amount
    q_next_start --> q_process_starts: more start assets
    q_next_start --> q_process_ends: no more start assets
    q_process_ends --> q_validate_end: for asset in endList
    q_validate_end --> q_check_auction_exists: validate auction exists
    q_check_auction_exists --> q_end_auction: live auction exists
    q_check_auction_exists --> q_revert_no_auction: no auction
    q_revert_no_auction --> [*]: revert NoActiveAuction
    q_end_auction --> q_return_remaining: delete s_auctionStarts[asset]
    q_return_remaining --> q_send_proceeds: transfer remaining asset balance to FeeAggregator
    q_send_proceeds --> q_next_end: transfer LINK proceeds to s_assetOutReceiver
    q_next_end --> q_process_ends: more end assets
    q_next_end --> [*]: no more end assets

    note right of q_start_auction
        INV-001: performUpkeep uses hard reverts unlike checkUpkeep soft skips
        INV-002: performUpkeep does NOT re-check elapsed duration or dust (allows forced endings)
        INV-003: Remaining auction assets are returned to FeeAggregator on end
        INV-004: LINK proceeds sent to s_assetOutReceiver (Reserves)
    end note
